name: Diep & Tank.io battle war - Deip the pro tank team
name_original: Diep & Tank.io battle war - Deip the pro tank team
description:
Play the simplest, but hardest game ever!

1. Tap to jump from one base to another without getting spotted
2. If you are going to crash, tap again to return back
3. Don't mess with US military land force.

4. Good luck. You will need it!
